+def to_date(value):
+    """转化为 datetime.date 类型"""
+    if not value:
+        return value
+    if isinstance(value, six.string_types):
+        date = value[:10]
+        try:
+            separator = date[4]
+            if separator in {'-', '/'}:
+                return datetime.date(*map(int, date.split(separator)))
+            else:
+                return datetime.date(int(value[:4]), int(value[4:6]), int(value[6:8]))
